<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=16562">everquest.allakhazam.com/...item=16562</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
From the link above, there are a lot of raid encounters level 65 or above.  I would like to have some advice where is good place to hunt for those runes?  I have a group of friends which are lvl 65 pally, ranger, druid, mage, rogue and myself.   Please recommend a place that we can handle or can have the spell rune dropped easily?  <br>
<br>
If all the runes are rare drop, where is good place to farm fast cast for one lvl 65 group?<br>
<br>
Thanks <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub136.ezboard.com/beqenchantersrealm.showUserPublicProfile?gid=astyd>astyd</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Enchanter Realm Master</span><br>  Posts: 172<br> <font color=#330000>(8/15/03 10:19 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=307.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Voice of Quellious (C 5)</span><hr size=1> <br>
Well now that is a tall order.<br>
<br>
Runes are rare drops unless you are in the Elemental Planes where they are a bit more common.<br>
<br>
Two places I have seen them drop are in BoT and Tactics.  I forget where in Tactics but there are some odd named in the Pit.  In BoT the same guys who can drop molds (i.e. mini-nameds) can drop Runes.  So, the best place to get Runes is in the ME camp on the Earth Side of BoT  (all this assumes you are not Elementally flagged).  Now the only problem with this answer is of course this is camped 24/7 (at least on my server).  After ME I guess, the Lightning side of BoT would be where I go next.<br>
<br>
I have not recommended Tactics because I have no idea if you are flagged for Tactics or not.<br>
<br>
Cames Houdini<br>
